full_text: Screened by NARA, 9/27/2023 TIONAL FORM 230 (English-Thai) (REV. 6-82) ) DEPARTMENT OF STATE DEPT. OF STATE APPLICATION FOR IMMIGRANT VISA AND ALIEN REGISTRATION of 2 TRUCTIONS: This form must be filled out in DUPLICATE by typewriter, or if by hand in legible block letters. ALL questions must answered, if applicable. Questions which are not applicable should be so marked. If there is insufficient room on the form, answer on eparate sheets, in duplicate using the same numbers as appear on the form. Attach the sheets to the forms. DO NOT SIGN this form un- til instructed to do so by the consular officer. The fee for filling this application for an immigrant visa is $25.00 The fee should be paid in United States dollars or local currency equivalent or by bank draft, when you appear before the consular officer. WARNING: Any false statement or concealment of a material fact may result in your permanent exclusion from the United States. Even though you should be admitted to the United States, a fraudulent entry could be grounds for your prosecution and/or deportation. d IDIAS 4 25.00 RITION 1.
